<node CREATED="1527090695285" ID="ID_1291098733" MODIFIED="1530116963582" TEXT="Iterators">
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <font size="1">Iterator is a fail-fast in nature. it throws <i>ConcurrentModificationException</i><br size="1" />if a collection is modified while iterating other than it&#8217;s own remove() method.<br size="1" />Whereas Enumeration is fail-safe in nature. It doesn&#8217;t throw any exceptions<br size="1" />if a collection is modified while iterating. </font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
<edge STYLE="bezier"/>
<node CREATED="1527090745042" ID="ID_112247914" MODIFIED="1527096639246" TEXT="failfast">
<richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <font size="1" face="Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(36, 39, 41)">&quot;Fail fast&quot; means: it&#160;</font><font size="15px" face="Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(36, 39, 41)"><em style="font-style: italic; margin-top: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; font-size: 15px; border-bottom-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-left: 0px; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-weight: 400; border-bottom-style: none; color: rgb(36, 39, 41); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; padding-bottom: 0px; border-left-style: none; vertical-align: baseline; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-right-style: none; text-align: left"><i>may</i></em></font><font size="1" face="Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(36, 39, 41)">&#160;fail ... and the failure condition is checked aggressively </font><font size="1"><br size="1" /></font><font size="1" face="Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(36, 39, 41)">so that the failure condition is (where possible) detected&#160;</font><font size="15px" face="Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(36, 39, 41)"><em style="font-style: italic; margin-top: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-left: 0px; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px; text-transform: none; font-family: Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; padding-top: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; border-bottom-style: none; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(36, 39, 41); margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; border-left-style: none; vertical-align: baseline; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-right-style: none; text-align: left"><i>before</i></em></font><font size="1" face="Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(36, 39, 41)">&#160;damage can be done. </font><font size="1"><br size="1" /></font><font size="1" face="Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(36, 39, 41)">In Java, a fail-fast iterator fails by throwing a&#160;</font><font size="13px" face="Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, Lucida Console, Liberation Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, Courier New, monospace, sans-serif" color="rgb(36, 39, 41)"><code style="font-style: normal; margin-top: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-right: 5px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(239, 240, 241); padding-left: 5px; text-indent: 0px; margin-right: 0px; text-transform: none; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, Lucida Console, Liberation Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Bitstream Vera Sans Mono, Courier New, monospace, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; padding-top: 1px; letter-spacing: normal; border-bottom-style: none; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(36, 39, 41); margin-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 1px; line-height: inherit; border-left-style: none; vertical-align: baseline; border-right-width: 0px; margin-left: 0px; border-top-style: none; border-right-style: none; text-align: left">ConcurrentModificationException</code></font><font size="1" face="Arial, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="rgb(36, 39, 41)">.</font>
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
